Steps for using Github
----------------------
-first of dwnload git exe from https://git-scm.com/download/win and install it on recommended settings.
-2nd right clk on folder area and select open with this folder with cmd
-3rd now on this stage git folder is empty, but after  

git init 		//create foldr of repository
git status 		//status of curnt postin
git clone [path] //
git add file_name. //to-add untrackfile
git commit -m "message will place here" // to-add comment
git log 		//to view commit history
git push 		// the folder content in which this command runs, will push to online repositry
git add .			// to add all file to repository
git add *.html		//by using wildcard, we only can add appropriate file extension files. 
touch .gitignore	// for create .gitignore file auto
